text: Heine Araújo (born ) is a retired Brazilian female artistic gymnast, who represented her nation at international competitions. She participated at the 2001 World Artistic Gymnastics Championships in Ghent, Belgium. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian female artistic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 1999 Pan American Games Category:Originators of elements in artistic gymnastics Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Brazil Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics
